::KitKat3:
She didn't show her disappointment.  She smiled instead,"That's 
alright. One can't jeopardize the current situation if that's the 
best thing for the pack."

DarkMouse::
She followed Dollen into the lunch room and ordered a nice cold 
liquid energon. "Ahh, just what a bot needs."

Feline::
She arrived and landed the shuttle.  She stepped out and looked at 
HotRod. "Uh, Hi. HOw are you doing?"  She turned and showed off her 
new form. "Like it?"
